latestPosts.caption:
A heartfelt thank you to Sombaria Police Station for choosing Halka Ramailo as the venue for the farewell programme of Miss Pushpa Kumari!

We feel truly honored to have hosted such a warm and memorable evening. We hope you all had a great time soaking in the vibes, enjoying the delicacies, and celebrating together!

Special thanks for loving our favorites —
Buff Sukuti 🐃, Halka Ramailo Chicken 🍗, Peanut Sadeko 🥜, and the full dinner spread 🍽️!

Your smiles and presence made the night even more special!
Wishing Miss Pushpa Kumari all the very best in her journey ahead — may success and happiness always be with you!

And to everyone reading this — whether it’s a birthday bash 🎉, anniversary celebration ❤️, farewell, or any special occasion —
Halka Ramailo is always ready to welcome you with great food, fun vibes, and heartfelt hospitality!

Thank you once again!
Stay Ramailo, always!

#HalkaRamailo #SombariaPoliceStation #FarewellVibes #BuffSukutiMagic #StayRamailo #CelebrateWithUs #Daramdin

Five years.💫Countless memories. A lifetime of friendship.
Today, you’re not just going to another place — you’re taking a piece of my heart with you👩‍❤️‍👩
From laughter to tears, secrets to dreams, we’ve shared it all.
No matter the distance, you’ll always be my bestie, my sister, my constant.
I’ll miss you more than words can say — 🤭but I’m so proud of you.
Here’s to the next chapter in your life... and to us, always
